column3: Please use a commit message that details the change, instead of just "Update .travis.yml"\n
You haven't updated the commit message, just the issue title, although that's also useful\n
What problem does this solve? The osx host won't always be "x86_64-apple-darwin11", and OSX_SDK is only set for osx builds. \n
thanks for remind, this pull request is a mistake, i have not noticed that OS_SDK var check. please reject and close it. thanks.\n
@imharrywu No problem, thanks for having a look!\n
